OL,5,ECHRISTMAS PRIZE DRAW                   
OL,6,BThe Write It compy continues as normal 
OL,7,Bthroughout December - BUT every entry  
OL,8,Bpublished has an extra prize chance.   
OL,10,BWe've gotETWO PACKARD-BELL PULSAR 20   
OL,11,Bcomputers,Bone for the winning entry   
OL,12,Band one for the winner's school. Each  
OL,13,Bhas aE200 MHz Intel processor, 3.2GB   
OL,14,Ehard driveBand loads of other features.
OL,16,BEachEChristmasBentry we publish on this
OL,17,Bpage and page 197 goes into the prize  
OL,18,Bdraw. Closing dateEDecember 31B1997 -  
OL,19,Bwinner announcedEJanuary 7 1998.       
